data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home nestled in a midtown neighborhood. With its classic design and beautiful hardwood floors throughout, this residence offers both comfort and style. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an inviting living room featuring the warmth of the hardwood floors and ample natural light streaming through the windows. The open layout seamlessly connects the living space to the adjacent dining area, creating an ideal setting for both daily living and entertaining. The kitchen boasts modern conveniences, including sleek countertops, updated cabinetry, and a range of appliances to cater to your culinary needs. The hardwood floors continue into the bedrooms, complementing the cozy ambiance. Additional features of this home include off-street parking, a patio, energy-efficient appliances, a large enclosed porch. With its desirable location, this home is conveniently situated near all conveniences, adding to the overall appeal of the property.
